      <hr/>
      <p>Improve the accuracy of your FollowBias by correcting the gender of the accounts you follow. Your corrections will improve all FollowBias data!</p>
      <p><strong>Please be sensitive to people's privacy</strong> by only revealing information that's already public. <strong>If the person you follow doesn't identify as male or female</strong> please do not reveal their gender. For those who prefer not to divulge or identify otherwise, please label those accounts as "brands, bots, &amp; more."</p>
      <p>Gender is more complex than male and female, although the birth data behind our algorithm only recognizes those categories. Balancing privacy with the nuances of identity is challenging; we encourage your feedback and recommendations.</p>
      <p>Here are examples of our gender estimations. Click "start corrections" to review everyone you follow. If the wrong category is highlighted, click the correct one to change it.</p>
      <p>Thank you in advance for your help and sensitivity!</p>

